  <brief_title>Remifentanil for Preventing Propofol Injection Pain in Elderly Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect-site Concentration of Remifentanil for Preventing Propofol Injection Pain in Elderly Patients: A Comparison With Adult Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
